Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:37.70,ED,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}I don't know why, all I know is there's something wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.12,0:21:43.58,ED,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}Every time I look at you, you seem so alive
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:49.96,ED,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}Tell me how do you do it, walk me through it
